DMT Denies Repubblica Report It’s Reached Deal With Berlusconi’s Mediaset

-- B y   J e r r o l d   C o l t e n
-- 
2011-07-20T07:18:27Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-20/dmt-denies-repubblica-report-it-s-reached-deal-with-berlusconi-s-mediaset.html
Digital Multimedia Technologies SpA (DMT) 
denied a press report that it has reached an agreement on a
merger of its tower activities, according to a statement sent
through the Italian stock exchange.  DMT said talks with  Mediaset SpA (MS)  are continuing and that
the deadline for exclusivity remains July 28.  Daily la Repubblica reported today that the companies
reached an agreement on a merger of their tower activities.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Jerrold Colten at 
 jcolten@bloomberg.net  